<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.5390.1.1>
    dc:creator "Bertani, Rogério" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Taxonomic revision and cladistic analysis of Lasiodora C. L. Koch, 1850 (Araneae, Theraphosidae) with notes on related genera" ;
    bibo:endPage "116" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-12-27" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "5390" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434522>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434524>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434618>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434620>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434622>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434626>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434630>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434632>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434636> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434522>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8–15. Stridulatory setae of prolateral coxa I, males. 8, L. parahybana, Brazil, state of Pernambuco, Cabo de Santo Agostinho. 9, L. sertaneja n. sp. (IBSP 4127B). 10, L. camurujipe n. sp. (MNRJ 7764). 11, L. franciscana n. sp. (IBSP 8050). 12, L. subcanens (IBSP 9546). 13, L. klugi (MNRJ 7742). 14, L. benedeni (IBSP 84328). 15, L. klugi, Brazil, state of Bahia, Ilhéus. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434522/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434524>
    dc:description "FIGURE 16. Strict consensus of three cladograms obtained with setk.run and concavity 7.8125. All characters non-additive. Fit = 7.38251, length = 161.30. Absolute/relative Bremer support are in each node. The names of the genera and species in the cladogram are in accordance with the results obtained in the cladistic analysis carried out here, and do not consider the new genera and transfers proposed by Galleti-Lima et al. 2023." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434524/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434618>
    dc:description "FIGURES 165─170. Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921. (165–169) male (IBSP 4758). (165–167) left palp bulb. 165, retrolateral. 166, prolateral. 167, dorsal. (168─169) left tibial apophysis. 168, ventral. 169, prolateral. 170, female (MZUSP 27621), spermathecae. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434620>
    dc:description "FIGURES 171─175. Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921, male (IBSP 4758), stridulatory apparatus. (171─172) left maxilla, retrolateral. 171, general view. 172, detail of spiniform setae on upper, middle and lower areas. (173─175) left coxa I, prolateral. 173, general view. 174, detail of stridulatory setae. 175, detail of area below suture. Scale bar = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434622>
    dc:description "FIGURES 176─180. Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921, female (MZUSP 27621), stridulatory apparatus. (176─177) left maxilla, retrolateral. 176, general view. 177, detail of spiniform setae on upper, middle and lower areas. (178─180) left coxa I, prolateral. 178, general view. 179, detail of stridulatory setae. 180, detail of area below suture. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434622/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434626>
    dc:description "FIGURES 187─192. Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921, male lectotype (MZUSP 132). (187─188) left palp bulb. 187, retrolateral. 188, prolateral. (189─190) left coxa I, prolateral. 189, general view. 190, detail of stridulatory setae. 191, left maxilla, retrolateral. 192, left tibial apophysis, ventral. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434626/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434630>
    dc:description "FIGURES 197─198. Lasiodora dulcicola Mello-Leitão, 1921, holotype immature male (MZUSP 142). 197, left coxa I, prolateral. 198, right maxilla, retrolateral. Scale bar = 1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434632>
    dc:description "FIGURES 199─200. Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921, live. 199, male, Vila Velha, state of Espírito Santo, Brazil. 200, female, São José do Calçado, state of Espírito Santo, Brazil. Photos: Rogério Bertani." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434632/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10434636>
    dc:description "FIGURES 201─202. Maps showing records of Lasiodora subcanens Mello-Leitão, 1921 in southeastern Brazil. 201, relief. 202, biomes. Forested areas on Fig. 202 are in green shades (Brazilian Atlantic Forest). Brown areas are of Cerrado. “?” represents dubious record." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10434636/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

